---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Kemitraan Epigrap — Jaringan Ekosistem Phygital"
  description="Bergabunglah dengan jaringan kemitraan Epigrap sebagai pengrajin monumen fisik atau afiliator agen pemasaran."
>
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <!-- Hero / Header -->
    <header class="partner-header text-center">
      <h1 class="brand-title">MITRA <span class="text-brass">EPIGRAP</span></h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Bangun keabadian bersama jaringan ekosistem phygital kami.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Cards Section -->
    <section class="partner-cards-section container">
      <div class="cards-grid">
        
        <!-- Card 1: Pengrajin -->
        <article class="partner-card card-dark">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <!-- Tool / Craftsman icon -->
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.77 3.77z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Mitra Pengrajin</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Tingkatkan nilai (added value) produk fisik buatan Anda dengan menambahkan teknologi Epigrap. Jadilah pemasok monumen phygital bersertifikasi di ekosistem kami.</p>
          
          <ul class="benefit-list">
            <li>Integrasi teknologi pada prasasti/batu/logam</li>
            <li>Inklusif untuk seniman pahat & vendor material</li>
            <li>Akses langsung ke basis klien premium</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/dasbor" class="btn-cta">GABUNG SEBAGAI PENGRAJIN</a>
        </article>

        <!-- Card 2: Affiliator -->
        <article class="partner-card card-light">
          <div class="icon-wrapper">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <!-- Network / marketing icon -->
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.19 8.688a4.5 4.5 0 0 1 1.242 7.244l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-6.364-6.364l1.757-1.757m13.35-.622 1.757-1.757a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-6.364-6.364l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 0 1.242 7.244"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="card-title">Agensi & Afiliator</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Buka gerbang penghasilan tanpa batas. Hubungkan solusi Epigrap dengan klien institusi, pemerintah, atau swasta dan raih komisi bagi hasil (revenue sharing) yang menarik.</p>
          
          <ul class="benefit-list">
            <li>Sistem Komisi (Revenue Share) dinamis</li>
            <li>Lisensi penjualan produk teknologi premium</li>
            <li>Dukungan materi pemasaran menyeluruh</li>
          </ul>

          <a href="/dasbor" class="btn-cta">GABUNG SEBAGAI AGEN</a>
        </article>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Kolaborasi Lain Section -->
    <section class="partner-cta-section container text-center">
      <h2 class="cta-title">Punya Ide Kolaborasi Lain?</h2>
      <p class="cta-desc">Apakah Anda mewakili institusi, komunitas sejarah, atau bisnis yang memiliki visi sama dalam melestarikan budaya? Kami sangat terbuka untuk berdiskusi dan menjajaki kerja sama strategis dengan Anda.</p>
      <a href="mailto:support@epigrap.com" class="btn-cta-alt">Hubungi Kami</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-wrapper {
    padding-top: 10rem;
    padding-bottom: 8rem;
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top center, rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.05) 0%, var(--color-obsidian) 70%);
  }

  .partner-header {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    animation: fadeDown 1s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .brand-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
    text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .text-brass {
    color: var(--color-brass);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.7);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .partner-card {
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease, border-color 0.4s;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease-out 0.3s forwards;
  }

  .partner-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    border-color: rgba(197,160,89,0.3);
  }

  /* Delay for second card */
  .partner-card:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 0.5s;
  }

  .card-dark {
    background: rgba(17, 17, 17, 0.8);
  }

  .card-light {
    background: rgba(30, 27, 20, 0.8); /* a bit warmer to match brass */
    border-color: rgba(197,160,89,0.15);
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-brass);
  }

  .icon-wrapper svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-desc {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .benefit-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    flex-grow: 1; /* Pushes button to bottom */
  }

  .benefit-list li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .benefit-list li::before {
    content: "✦";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 1px;
    color: var(--color-brass);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .btn-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-brass);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-brass);
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-brass);
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.4);
  }

  .text-center {
    text-align: center;
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @keyframes fadeDown {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Kolaborasi Lain Section */
  .partner-cta-section {
    margin-top: 5rem;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    animation: fadeUp 1s ease-out 0.7s forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-parchment);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .cta-desc {
    color: rgba(244, 238, 223, 0.7);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    max-width: 650px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .btn-cta-alt {
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--color-brass);
    color: var(--color-obsidian);
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-cta-alt:hover {
    background: rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.85);
    box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(197, 160, 89, 0.4);
  }
</style>
